<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">الْمُوازَنَةُ بين الْفاعِلِ والْمَفْعُولِ بهِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأمثلة:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١- يَجُرُّ الحِصانُ العَجَلَةَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢- قَطفَ الْغُلامُ الزَّهْرَةَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣- رَبَطتْ فاطِمةُ الْجَدْيَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٤- يَسْقِي الْفلاَّحُ الزَّرْعَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٥- قَذفَ اللاَّعِبُ الْكُرَةَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٦- حبَسَ الشُّرْطيُّ اللِّصَّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">النَّتائجُ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عَرفْنا مما مَضى،<span class="c5"> ونَعْرِفُ مِنْ تَأَمُّلِ الأَمثلةِ السَّابقةِ ما يأْتي:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١- أَنَّ كلَّ فاعِلٍ وكلَّ مَفْعُولٍ بهِ اسْمٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢- أَنَّ الْفاعِلَ هوَ الذي صَدَرَ عَنْهُ الْفِعْلُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٣- أَنَّ الْمفْعُولَ بهِ هُوَ الَّذِي وقع عليه الفعل.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٤- أَنَّ الْفَاعِلَ آخِرُهُ مرفوع.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٥- أن المفعول به آخِرُهُ مَنْصُوبٌ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>